---
import Layout from "../../Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Practice">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-xl space-y-6 px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h1 class="font-semibold text-2xl">Privacy Policy for Practice</h1>
      <p class="text-sm opacity-60">Last updated: December 19, 2024</p>
    </div>

    <p>
      Practice ("we", "our", or "us") operates the Practice: Habit Tracker
      mobile application.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl">Data Collection and Usage</h2>
      <p>
        Practice does not collect, store, or share any personal information or
        user data. We do not require you to create an account or sign in to use
        the app.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl">iCloud Sync and Data Storage</h2>
      <p>
        The app uses Apple's iCloud service to sync your habit data across your
        devices.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li>
          All habit data and statistics are stored in your personal iCloud
          account and locally on your device.
        </li>
        <li>
          We never have access to this data, and it is never transmitted to our
          servers or any third parties.
        </li>
        <li>
          If iCloud is disabled or unavailable, your data remains stored
          locally on your device.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Practice does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or
        tracking services. Your data stays entirely within your control.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl">Permissions</h2>
      <p>The app may request the following permissions:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li>
          <strong>iCloud / CloudKit</strong>: To sync your habits and progress
          across your Apple devices.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be
        reflected in app updates and on this page.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us
        at <a
          href="mailto:hello@praveenjuge.com"
          class="underline decoration-2 underline-offset-1"
        >
          hello@praveenjuge.com
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
